      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of April 13 review of film Lonely Hearts; character who commits suicide shoots herself</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A film review in Weekend on Friday about ''Lonely Hearts'' referred incorrectly to the suicide of the wife of the central character, the detective Elmer Robinson. She shoots herself; she does not slash her wrists.</p>
      </block>
